data.title: WOW! Detroit Channel Lineups
data.meta_description: WOW! Detroit Channel Lineups - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides a channel lineup for various cable TV packages from WOW!. It lists over 200 channels across basic cable, digital/HD cable, premium channels, music channels, PPV/on demand options. It also includes notes about channel positions being subject to change and needing an HD equipment to view HD channels.
